<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$wu-bin-61-98" href="/people/wu-bin-61-98">吴斌</a>，<strong title="我就看看不说话" class="zu-question-my-bio">我就看看不说话</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="4">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$cha-hai-jun" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/cha-hai-jun" class="zg-link" title="査海军">査海军</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xie-yun-long-49" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xie-yun-long-49" class="zg-link" title="叶云龙">叶云龙</a></span>
